description:
In this edition of We've Only Just Begun To Trend, Jack and Miles discuss Steve Harvey's new and improved style, Kyrie Irving breaks his silence, Joe Rogan v. Sanjay Gupta, how global shortages are Joe Biden's fault (somehow), Dodgers v. Giants game 5, and the eternal question: Karen Carpenter or Madonna.
